<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:w="urn:import:fr.putnami.pwt.core.widget.client"
	xmlns:c="urn:import:fr.putnami.pwt.plugin.code.client">

	<ui:import field="fr.putnami.pwt.plugin.code.client.configuration.xml.XmlConfiguration.XML_CONFIGURATION" />

	<ui:with field="navSpy" type="fr.putnami.pwt.core.widget.client.NavSpy" />

	<w:HTMLPanel>
		<w:Heading level="2" navSpy="{navSpy}">Carousel</w:Heading>
		<p class="lead">We provide a full bootstrap's Carousel support, allowing auto-play, pause on hover and display left and right navigation buttons.</p>
					
		<w:Heading level="3" >Basic usage</w:Heading>
		<p>Add some <code>CarouselItem</code> to the <code>Carousel</code>. A <code>CarouselItem</code> is a <code>HTMLPanel</code> which can also have a <code>caption</code> child to add some caption to the item. The caption has to be a <code>IsWidget</code>.</p>
		<p>Use the <code>autoPlay</code> property to enable autoPlay. By default, the <code>pauseOnHover</code> property is set to <code>true</code>. You can customize the delay with the <code>timerDelay</code> property (default set to 5000 ms).</p>
		<p>Use the <code>displayNavButtons</code> property to show / hide the left and right navs buttons (default set to <code>true</code>).</p>
		<div class="showcase-sample-block">
			<div class="showcase-sample">
				<w:Carousel>
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="First slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
					</w:CarouselItem>
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="Second slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
						<w:caption>
							<w:Container tag="div">
								<w:Heading level="2">Item caption Title</w:Heading>						
								<w:Text>Item caption</w:Text>
							</w:Container>
						</w:caption>
					</w:CarouselItem>
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="Third slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
					</w:CarouselItem>
				</w:Carousel>
				<br/>
				<br/>
				<w:Carousel autoPlay="true" timerDelay="2500" displayNavButtons="false">
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="First slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
					</w:CarouselItem>
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="Second slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
						<w:caption>
							<w:Container tag="div">
								<w:Heading level="2">Item caption Title</w:Heading>						
								<w:Text>Item caption</w:Text>
							</w:Container>
						</w:caption>
					</w:CarouselItem>
					<w:CarouselItem>
						<img alt="Third slide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"/>
					</w:CarouselItem>
				</w:Carousel>
			</div>
			<c:StaticCode configuration="{XML_CONFIGURATION}">
<pre><![CDATA[
<w:Carousel>
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="First slide" src="..."/>
	</w:CarouselItem>
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="Second slide" src="..."/>
		<w:caption>
			<w:Container tag="div">
				<w:Heading level="2">Item caption Title</w:Heading>
				<w:Text>Item caption</w:Text>
			</w:Container>
		</w:caption>
	</w:CarouselItem>
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="Third slide" src="..."/>
	</w:CarouselItem>
</w:Carousel>

<w:Carousel autoPlay="true" timerDelay="2500" displayNavButtons="false">
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="First slide" src="..."/>
	</w:CarouselItem>
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="Second slide" src="..."/>
		<w:caption>
			<w:Container tag="div">
				<w:Heading level="2">Item caption Title</w:Heading>
				<w:Text>Item caption</w:Text>
			</w:Container>
		</w:caption>
	</w:CarouselItem>
	<w:CarouselItem>
		<img alt="Third slide" src="..."/>
	</w:CarouselItem>
</w:Carousel>]]></pre>
			</c:StaticCode>
		</div>
	</w:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder>